EXPRESSION: CASE WHEN COALESCE(IX_IXQDWLOS_1_0.EXPIRY_DATE,'') <> ''  AND IX_IXQDWLOS_1_0.EXPIRY_DATE <> '2069-12-31'  THEN to_date(TRIM(IX_IXQDWLOS_1_0.EXPIRY_DATE),'yyyy-MM-dd') WHEN IX_IXQDWLOS_1_0.EXPIRY_DATE = '2069-12-31' THEN to_date('9999-12-31','yyyy-MM-dd') ELSE to_date('1000-01-03','yyyy-MM-dd') END
